                                <li>Documentation provided with deliverables</li>
                                <li>Development updates through agreed communication channels</li>
                                <li>Technical guidance for deployment and launch</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">e) Quality Standards</h4>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-4">
                                <li>Code review and testing throughout development</li>
                                <li>Security best practices implementation</li>
                                <li>Performance optimization</li>
                                <li>Responsive design across all devices</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
