                </div>

                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">4. Payment Terms</h2>
                    <div class="ml-4 space-y-4">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">4.1. Developer as Subscription</h3>
                        <div class="ml-4 space-y-4">
                            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">a) Billing Terms</h4>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-4">
                                <li>Subscription fees charged at the beginning of each billing period</li>
                                <li>All fees are non-refundable for the current period</li>
                                <li>Subscription can be canceled at any time</li>
                                <li>Access continues until the end of the paid period</li>
                                <li>Option to pause subscription available for extended payment periods</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">b) Failed Payments</h4>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-4">
                                <li>Service access may be suspended upon payment failure</li>
                                <li>Notification will be sent regarding failed payments</li>
                                <li>Resolution required to restore service access</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">4.2. App Packages</h3>
                        <div class="ml-4 space-y-4">
                            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">a) Payment Structure</h4>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-4">
                                <li>Full payment required upfront at the time of package purchase</li>
                                <li>All payments are non-refundable</li>
                                <li>Development begins after payment confirmation</li>
                                <li>No hidden fees or additional charges unless agreed upon in writing</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">5. Intellectual Property Rights</h2>
                    <div class="ml-4 space-y-4">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">5.1. Ownership</h3>
                        <div class="ml-4 space-y-4">
