                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-4">
                                <li>Full ownership of custom code created specifically for the Client</li>
                                <li>Rights to all project deliverables upon full payment</li>
                                <li>Access to delivered code repositories maintained after service termination</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">b) Company Rights</h4>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-4">
