                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">6.3. Code Delivery</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-4">
                            <li>Code delivered through private GitHub repositories</li>
                            <li>Documentation included with deliverables</li>
                            <li>Access to repositories maintained after service completion</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">7. Service Limitations and Guarantees</h2>
                    <div class="ml-4 space-y-4">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">7.1. Service Limitations</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-4">
                            <li>Concurrent task limits based on subscription tier</li>
                            <li>Development using Primary Technology Stack (Section 2.3.a)</li>
