                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-4">
                            <li>No guarantee of uninterrupted service</li>
                            <li>No warranty for third-party services or integrations</li>
                            <li>Results dependent on provided requirements and specifications</li>
                            <li>Development timelines subject to task complexity</li>
