                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">8.2. Security Practices</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-4">
                            <li>Secure code repositories</li>
                            <li>Industry-standard security protocols</li>
                            <li>Protected access to development environments</li>
                            <li>Regular security updates and maintenance</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">9. Service Termination</h2>
                    <div class="ml-4 space-y-4">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">9.1. Subscription Termination</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-4">
                            <li>Client may cancel subscription at any time</li>
                            <li>No refunds for current billing period</li>
                            <li>Access maintained until end of paid period</li>
