                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">10. Modifications to Terms</h2>
                    <div class="ml-4 space-y-4">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">10.1. Terms Updates</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-4">
                            <li>Company reserves right to modify terms</li>
                            <li>30 days notice for material changes</li>
                            <li>Notice provided via email</li>
                            <li>Continued use constitutes acceptance</li>
                            <li>Right to terminate if changes are unacceptable</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">10.2. Service Modifications</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-4">
                            <li>Right to modify service features with notice</li>
                            <li>Right to adjust pricing with 30 days notice</li>
                            <li>Existing packages honored at original terms</li>
                            <li>Subscription changes effective next billing cycle</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">11. Dispute Resolution</h2>
                    <div class="ml-4 space-y-4">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">11.1. Governing Law</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-4">
                            <li>These Terms governed by Polish law</li>
                            <li>EU consumer protection laws apply where relevant</li>
